Description: This is a 100% authentic Foley and Corinna "La Trenza" city tote in EUC. I only carried it once! It is in black leather and can be carried by the handles or folded over and carried over the shoulder. It's a celebrity bag - see Halle Berry carrying something similar! It's classic with lots of versatility. I frankly have too many black bags, which is why I'm selling it, but I do love it. This particular style has whipstitching on the side, with grommets, making it a bit more downtown and edgy. Currently sold out - I paid over $300 for it, so I'm listing it for a fraction of that. Bought at Bloomingdale's. Stored in my smoke-free home. I will send it along with its dust bag.
